.
├── app/
│   ├── main.py            # FastAPI application
│   ├── models.py          # SQLAlchemy models for the database
│   ├── database.py        # Database configuration
│   └── Dockerfile         # Docker setup for the FastAPI app
├── docker-compose.yml     # Docker Compose setup for the entire environment
├── README.md              # Project documentation (this file)
└── requirements.txt       # Python dependencies


API Endpoints

GET	/products	Get a list of all products
GET	/product/{product_id}	Get details of a specific product
POST	/product	Create a new product
PUT	/product/{product_id}	Update an existing product
DELETE	/product/{product_id}	Delete a product

